<h1>骂</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">mà</span><span class=alesi>(ma4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 骂 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 骂</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/accuse" style="color:black;">accuse</a>, <a href="/dictionary/blame" style="color:black;">blame</a>, <a href="/dictionary/curse" style="color:black;">curse</a>, scold</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 9<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 9 strokes: <a href="/character/是" title="shi4: indeed, yes, right; to be; demonstrative pronoun, this, that">是</a>, <a href="/character/说" title="shuo1: speak, say, talk; scold, upbraid">说</a>, <a href="/character/要" title="yao4: necessary, essential; necessity">要</a>, <a href="/character/种" title="zhong3: seed; race, breed; to plant">种</a>, <a href="/character/面" title="mian4: face; surface; plane; side, dimension">面</a>, <a href="/character/看" title="kan4: look, see; examine, scrutinize">看</a>, <a href="/character/前" title="qian2: in front, forward; preceding">前</a>, <a href="/character/点" title="dian3: dot, speck, spot; point, degree">点</a>, <a href="/character/将" title="jiang1: will, going to, future; general">将</a>, <a href="/character/很" title="hen3: very, quite, much">很</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/口" title="Kangxi radical 30">口</a>&nbsp;30.6</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/赏" title="shang3: reward, grant, bestow; appreciate">赏</a>, <a href="/character/颗" title="ke1: grain, kernel">颗</a>, <a href="/character/幅" title="fu2: piece, strip, breadth of, hem">幅</a>, <a href="/character/贴" title="tie1: paste to, stick on; attached to">贴</a>, <a href="/character/矛" title="mao2: spear, lance; KangXi radical 110">矛</a>, <a href="/character/腰" title="yao1: waist; kidney">腰</a>, <a href="/character/眉" title="mei2: eyebrows; upper margin of book">眉</a>, <a href="/character/碍" title="ai4: obstruct, hinder, block, deter">碍</a>, <a href="/character/敏" title="min3: fast, quick, clever, smart">敏</a>, <a href="/character/恋" title="lian4: love; long for, yearn for; love">恋</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" title="List of HSK 5 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 5 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 1449</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 1505</p><p><b>Traditional variant:</b> <a href="/character/罵">罵</a></p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/侮骂" title="wu3 ma4">侮骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/叱骂" title="chi4 ma4">叱骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/咒骂" title="zhou4 ma4">咒骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/唾骂" title="tuo4 ma4">唾骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/国骂" title="guo2 ma4">国骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/大骂" title="da4 ma4">大骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/对骂" title="dui4 ma4">对骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/怒骂" title="nu4 ma4">怒骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/耻骂" title="chi3 ma4">耻骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/恶骂" title="e4 ma4">恶骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/打骂" title="da3 ma4">打骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/挨骂" title="ai2 ma4">挨骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/斥骂" title="chi4 ma4">斥骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/漫骂" title="man4 ma4">漫骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/滥骂" title="lan4 ma4">滥骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/痛骂" title="tong4 ma4">痛骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/笞骂" title="chi1 ma4">笞骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/骂人" title="ma4 ren2">骂人</a>, <a href="/dictionary/骂名" title="ma4 ming2">骂名</a>, <a href="/dictionary/骂街" title="ma4 jie1">骂街</a>, <a href="/dictionary/臭骂" title="chou4 ma4">臭骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/詈骂" title="li4 ma4">詈骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/诟骂" title="gou4 ma4">诟骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/谩骂" title="man4 ma4">谩骂</a>, <a href="/dictionary/责骂" title="ze2 ma4">责骂</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">罵|骂[<span style="color:#000099;">mà</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- to scold<br>- to abuse<br>- to curse<br>- CL:<a href="/dictionary/通">通</a>[tong4],<a href="/dictionary/頓">